videos.description: Walker Kessler drives to the rim and finishes in traffic for Auburn.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Auburn's Walker Kessler finishes strong for and-1 bucket) 2021/12/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Auburn's Walker Kessler finishes strong for and-1 bucket

videos.description: LSU calls a timeout after Allen Flanigan drills a 3-pointer in transition to give Auburn a big lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Flanigan's triple puts Auburn ahead 18-1) 2021/12/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Flanigan's triple puts Auburn ahead 18-1

videos.description: LSU's Tari Eason does it all to snap an 18-0 Auburn run, stealing the ball on defense and taking it all the way for an and-1.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Eason takes steal coast to coast for LSU basket) 2021/12/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Eason takes steal coast to coast for LSU basket

videos.description: Auburn freshman Jabari Smith shows off his skills with a smooth 3-pointer with a hand in his face.

videos.headline: Jabari Smith drains off-the-dribble 3 for Auburn

videos.description: LSU's Darius Days heaves up a prayer that splashes in as the shot clock buzzer goes off.

videos.headline: Days hits spinning 3-ball to beat the shot clock for LSU

videos.description: LSU denies Auburn's alley-oop attempt and then Xavier Pinson dishes a behind-the-back pass to Tari Eason for the slam.
